name: Luke Skywalker
attackDescription: Luke enhances his speed and Pushes enemies away.

name: Yoda
attackDescription: Yoda unleashes the Force in an area in front of him, damaging and pushing foes.

name: Darth Maul
attackDescription: High velocity lightsaber spin attack, cutting down enemies in his path as he leaps forward.

name: Boba Fett
attackDescription: Boba Fett disappears from enemy radar, gains unlimited jet pack fuel, and acquires insight into the location of nearby foes.

name: Captain Phasma
attackDescription: This tool can blast enemies at far distances, while including a shock functionality for close targets.

name: Rey
attackDescription: Rey takes a moment to deeply sense her surroundings, revealing and highlighting all nearby enemies.

name: Finn
attackDescription: Finn focuses and targets one enemy in front of him, making sure every shot counts.

name: Palpatine
attackDescription: The area around The Emperor is charged with Force energy, damaging and slowing foes.

name: Han Solo
attackDescription: Han throws a sticky explosive that can be detonated at will.

name: Chewbacca
attackDescription: With a mighty roar, Chewbacca overcharges his Bowcaster, allowing him to fire full-power shots with no charge time.

name: Darth Vader
attackDescription: Vader uses his iconic Force choke to lift, damage, and drop enemies.

name: Leia Organa
attackDescription: Leia launches a stream of blaster fire.

name: Lando Calrissian
attackDescription: Lando takes focus and unloads powerful shots on up to five enemies.

name: Bossk
attackDescription: Bossk gains heat vision and enhanced strength as he loads high-damage micro grenades.

name: Anakin Skywalker
attackDescription: Anakin’s powers intensify whenever he and any nearby allies are attacked, building towards the ultimate punishment of a swift and inescapable grip seizing all enemies around him.

name: Obi-Wan Kenobi
attackDescription: A Jedi’s mastery of the Force can influence the weak-minded, and in the case of Master Kenobi, even subvert his enemy’s desire to dodge his attacks and use their abilities against him.

name: Kylo Ren
attackDescription: Kylo Ren immobilizes enemies in front of him.
